{"tid":1499300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為一個香港人我發現自己都唔係好瞭解香港人","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:42:25.000Z","uid":73972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98281d1e629a107e5e348a31582f7ffc89f0450e","tid":1499300,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"估唔到有一大班香港人係咁團結同熱血，估唔到今晚人鏈活動都咁成功"},{"pid":"5df413878e291c23fe934a968626a9513f0602a3","tid":1499300,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"我睇錯大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e33f1e2c1d728a2d047f0803480337c26fce26","tid":1499300,"uid":245016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢兩個月先真正認識到香港人同覺得自己係一個香港人!"},{"pid":"02b6922c45a08842c007c61c138e67492e65c860","tid":1499300,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"呢兩個幾月我先知有班香港人係咁勇敢，尤其一班前線既人，面對來勢洶洶同配哂槍既差佬，明知以卵擊石，都展示出無比既勇氣，令小弟佩服到五體投地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0718aabd04a22b08d082b116261fb61283cf5c63","tid":1499300,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"係一位前線巴打,有一個心願想大家幫幫我...<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dHsatT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dHsatT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借位推我嘅一個小心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月之前我都成日笑香港人on9,掃前雪,<br />\n開始做前線先知原來大家咁有heart"},{"pid":"55c2dea138b8d75f73c5bdbb1d58aaf26f5a12c2","tid":1499300,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"由6月9開始，我先真正認識香港人。<br />\n一直覺得香港人冷漠，係各家自掃門前雪嘅自私鬼。<br />\n點知，哩兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成日羨慕日本仔民族意志好強好團結，原來香港人有過之而無不及。<br />\n日本仔自己話佢哋喺從眾心理，但香港人唔係，救護車分人海，自發執垃圾，自發捐錢，自發派傳單等等，唔係從眾，而係出自真心。<br />\n我想信好多人都係因為驚冇人做，然後去做，結果發現，大家都係咁諗。<br />\n特別係嘢食，物資，周街派，但冇人拎，因為大家心都諗：留備更需要嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴線，邊度黎嘅質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}